Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Actress Yoon Jin Seo coolly admits she's currently dating on 'Life Bar' By beansss 1 hour ago 3,316 295 0 0 SEE ALSO: 10 Groups you didn't know that are masters of acapella 
She talked with the MCs about her love for surfing, even though the MCs seemed more interested in what type of guys she likes than her surfing adventures. While she and the MCs exchanged back and forth about surfing and meeting guys while surfing, Tak Jae Hoon asked, "What style of guy do you like?" 
Yoon Jin Seo answered, "Oh, I have a boyfriend." She admitted that her current boyfriend is also a surfer, and that she met him in the water while waiting for a wave. She elaborated with, "I was such an amateur at the time, so he asked me, 'Do you want me to teach you?'" 
After the broadcast, her label FNC Entertainment also shared on her behalf, "Yoon Jin Seo's boyfriend is a non-celebrity. It is her personal matter, so we don't know much beyond that."
